------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âš™ï¸ 4. Step-by-Step Implementation

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Step 1: Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install crewai
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Step 2: Define Agents (`agents.py`)

```python
from crewai import Agent

planner = Agent(
    role="Project Planner",
    goal="Break the user topic into structured research steps",
    backstory="Expert in AI project planning",
    verbose=True
)

researcher = Agent(
    role="AI Research Specialist",
    goal="Collect accurate and up-to-date information",
    backstory="Experienced AI analyst",
    verbose=True
)

writer = Agent(
    role="Technical Writer",
    goal="Create a clear and structured report",
    backstory="Professional AI content writer",
    verbose=True
)

reviewer = Agent(
    role="Quality Reviewer",
    goal="Improve clarity, structure, and correctness",
    backstory="Senior editor with AI expertise",
    verbose=True
)
```

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Step 3: Define Tasks (`tasks.py`)

```python
from crewai import Task
from agents import planner, researcher, writer, reviewer

plan_task = Task(
    description="Create a research plan for the topic.",
    expected_output="Step-by-step structured plan.",
    agent=planner
)

research_task = Task(
    description="Research the topic thoroughly.",
    expected_output="Detailed findings with key insights.",
    agent=researcher
)

write_task = Task(
    description="Write a full structured report.",
    expected_output="Formatted report with headings and bullet points.",
    agent=writer
)

review_task = Task(
    description="Review and improve the report.",
    expected_output="Final polished version.",
    agent=reviewer
)
```

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Step 4: Create the Crew (`crew.py`)

```python
from crewai import Crew
from agents import planner, researcher, writer, reviewer
from tasks import plan_task, research_task, write_task, review_task

crew = Crew(
    agents=[planner, researcher, writer, reviewer],
    tasks=[plan_task, research_task, write_task, review_task],
    verbose=True
)
```

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ Step 5: Run the System (`main.py`)

```python
from crew import crew

result = crew.kickoff(inputs={"topic": "Latest trends in Agentic AI"})
print(result)
```

