ğŸ“Œ 7. How to Upgrade This Project

You can improve it by adding:

* Web search tool
* Vector database (RAG)
* Shared memory
* Hierarchical process
* AgentOps monitoring
* Local LLM via Ollama

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âš ï¸ Common Beginner Mistakes

* Vague task descriptions
* Overlapping agent roles
* Too many agents
* No clear expected output
* Not testing agents individually

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ¯Key Takeaways

* CrewAI enables team-based AI systems
* Clear roles improve output quality
* Structured tasks reduce hallucination
* Multi-agent systems are scalable
* This is production-style Agentic AI
